      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/how-to-create-a-screenshot/</guid>
      <description>To create a screenshot, press the Print Screen button on Windows or Command + Shift + 4 on Mac, then edit and save the image. For mobile devices, press the Power and Volume-down buttons simultaneously on Android or the Sleep/Wake and Home buttons on iPhone.</description>
    </item>
