      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/how-to-take-a-screenshot/</guid>
      <description>To take a screenshot, press the Print Screen button on Windows or Command + Shift + 4 on Mac, then paste into an image editor to save. For mobile devices, press the Power and Volume-down buttons simultaneously on Android or the Side button and Volume-up button on iPhone.</description>
    </item>
